ull wp-image-3768438" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BST-Kylie@2000x2000.jpg" alt="凯莉·米洛 BST 海德公园海报。" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BST-Kylie@2000x2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BST-Kylie@2000x2000-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BST-Kylie@2000x2000-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BST-Kylie@2000x2000-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BST-Kylie@2000x2000-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BST-Kylie@2000x2000-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BST-Kylie@2000x2000-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3768438" class="wp-caption-text">凯莉·米洛 BST 海德公园海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h3><strong>以下是 2024 年 BST 海德公园凯莉·米洛 (Kylie Minogue) 的完整行程：</strong></h3><p><strong>大橡树舞台</strong><br /><strong>3:15pm-3:45pm – 阿尔特戈</strong><br /><strong>4:15pm-4:55pm – 艾拉·亨德森</strong><br /><strong>5:25pm-6:10pm – 阿尼塔</strong><br /><strong>6:50 PM - 7:50 PM – 码头</strong><br /><strong>8:50pm-10:20pm – 凯莉·米洛</strong></p><p><strong>彩虹舞台</strong><br /><strong>下午 3:45-4:15 – 弗雷德·罗伯茨</strong><br /><strong>4:55pm-5:25pm – ADMT</strong><br /> <strong>6:10pm-6:55pm – 汤姆·拉斯穆森</strong><br /><strong><br />鸟笼舞台<br />3:45pm-4:15pm – 格蕾丝·加肖<br />4:55pm-5:25pm – 现在说<br />6:10pm-6:40pm – 腮红<br /></strong></p><p><strong>古巴车库舞台</strong><br /><strong>3:45pm-4:15pm – 现场嘉年华</strong><br /><strong>4:55pm-5:25pm – 现场嘉年华</strong><br /><strong>6:10pm-6:45pm – 古巴兄弟</strong><br /><strong>7:50pm-8:45pm – 古巴兄弟</strong></p><p>您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/kylie-minogue-tickets/artist/735661?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wwEzBLW-RxyPWNIXqSXj8x-BUkCxFDSWcSNiXA0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_28