w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Falcon_And_The_Winter_Soldier_Sam_Wilson_Mackie-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Falcon_And_The_Winter_Soldier_Sam_Wilson_Mackie-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Falcon_And_The_Winter_Soldier_Sam_Wilson_Mackie-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Falcon_And_The_Winter_Soldier_Sam_Wilson_Mackie-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em>《美国队长：美丽新世界》</em>的第一部官方<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O_A8HdCDaWM&amp;t=1s" target="_blank" rel="noopener">预告片</a>已经发布，预告了大量的动作、多个新敌人和红浩克——你可以在上面观看。</p><p>在该系列的第四部电影<em>《美丽新世界》</em>中，安东尼·麦凯回归饰演山姆·威尔逊（又名“猎鹰”），在<a href="https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;opi=89978449&amp;url=https://www.nme.com/films/avengers-endgame&amp;ved=2ahUKEwicpPGm7aGHAxXEU0EAHSdMBhcQFnoECB8QAQ&amp;usg=AOvVaw0gjkBxxthEXwXeail1sb1Q"><em>《复仇者联盟：终局之战》</em></a>结束后，史蒂夫·罗杰斯（ <a href="https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;opi=89978449&amp;url=https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-evans&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjemomc7aGHAxVTV0EAHd6vCs8QFnoECBMQAQ&amp;usg=AOvVaw3iV90u99XAsuu5g6qXN9jc">克里斯·埃文斯</a>饰）和平退休，山姆·威尔逊接过了美国队长的衣钵。</p><p>继<a href="https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;opi=89978449&amp;url=https://www.nme.com/series/the-falcon-and-the-winter-soldier&amp;ved=2ahUKEwj0koyw7aGHAxXrUkEAHS1WB9sQFnoECBEQAQ&amp;usg=AOvVaw16m5e4f1-ja9NxO19jw4WH" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《猎鹰与冬日战士》</em></a>事件之后，新电影中山姆受命由新当选的美国总统撒迪厄斯·罗斯（<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harrison-ford">哈里森·福特</a>，接替已故的威廉·赫特饰）组建一支新的复仇者联盟。 </p><figure id="attachment_2928162" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2928162" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-2928162" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Cap__Bucky_Falcon_And_The_Winter_Soldier.jpg" alt="美国队长" width="2000" 