兰队公布了他们最喜欢的歌曲：“皮克福德的音乐太可怕了！”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/England-FCs-Ezri-Konsa-Phil-Foden-and-Jordan-Pickford.-Credit-Etsuo-Hara-Marcel-van-Dorst-and-James-Gill-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="英格兰足球俱乐部的埃兹里·康萨、菲尔·福登和乔丹·皮克福德。图片来源：Etsuo Hara、Marcel van Dorst 和 James Gill，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/England-FCs-Ezri-Konsa-Phil-Foden-and-Jordan-Pickford.-Credit-Etsuo-Hara-Marcel-van-Dorst-and-James-Gill-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/England-FCs-Ezri-Konsa-Phil-Foden-and-Jordan-Pickford.-Credit-Etsuo-Hara-Marcel-van-Dorst-and-James-Gill-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/England-FCs-Ezri-Konsa-Phil-Foden-and-Jordan-Pickford.-Credit-Etsuo-Hara-Marcel-van-Dorst-and-James-Gill-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/England-FCs-Ezri-Konsa-Phil-Foden-and-Jordan-Pickford.-Credit-Etsuo-Hara-Marcel-van-Dorst-and-James-Gill-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/England-FCs-Ezri-Konsa-Phil-Foden-and-Jordan-Pickford.-Credit-Etsuo-Hara-Marcel-van-Dorst-and-James-Gill-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/England-FCs-Ezri-Konsa-Phil-Foden-and-Jordan-Pickford.-Credit-Etsuo-Hara-Marcel-van-Dorst-and-James-Gill-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>英格兰男子足球俱乐部的成员透露了他们目前在训练营训练时听的歌曲。</p><p>在出现在<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0j9gl1q">BBC 的<em>《足球每日播客》</em></a>中时，当前球队分享了他们目前正在重复播放的歌曲。科尔·帕尔默 (Cole Palmer) 表示，他正在听<a href="/artists/Lil-Baby">Lil Baby</a>和 Byron Messia 的《Choppa》。 Ezri Konsa 和 Bukayo Saka 都表示，他们目前正在即兴演奏<a href="/artists/Tems">Tems</a>的《Love Me Jeje》，后者表示这首歌“真是一种氛围，伙计”。当被问到赛前是否听这首歌时，萨卡回答说：“几乎每天都听。”</p><p>菲尔·福登说：“歌迷们正在为我唱这首新英格兰歌曲”，指的是《菲尔·福登的火》——改编自<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀</a>的《黑暗中跳舞》。 “我想我已经重复了这句话，它深深地印在我的脑海里。每次我出现在体育场并听到它时，这都是，是的，一个超现实的时刻。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9PJUj8Anv6/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.